WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
NYUAD is an open campus which members of the public are welcome to visit

00:03.000 --> 00:08.000
As such, when students are in public areas of the university, they are expected to dress modestly, in accordance with local custom

00:08.000 --> 00:10.000
Dressing modestly is defined as keeping your shoulders and knees covered

00:10.000 --> 00:12.000
Dressing modestly does not include covering your hair

